Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • Car

  • public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    Following Java class Car includes and is identified by its registration number. A registration number always starts with a capital letter, followed by a four-digit number e.g. “T2345”. A car should have an owner and knows if it has been registered for a disabled driver.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pravin Bendre
